characterDescription.skinTone: fair skin with pink undertones, especially prominent on cheeks and forehead
characterDescription.eyeColor: bright sky blue eyes with slight darker limbal ring
characterDescription.eyeShape: large, almond-shaped eyes, slightly downturned at the outer corners, giving a serious expression, upper eyelids slightly hooded
characterDescription.hairColor: dark auburn brown with subtle hints of copper highlights especially towards the ends
characterDescription.hairTexture: fine, slightly wavy with tendency to curl, particularly around the face
characterDescription.hairStyle: Styled in two high pigtail buns, each secured with pink clip-on hair accessories, with loose wisps and curls framing the face
characterDescription.faceShape: round face with soft features, full cheeks, and a gently rounded jawline
characterDescription.nose: small, slightly upturned nose with a rounded tip
characterDescription.lips: medium-sized lips with a slightly fuller bottom lip, natural rosy pink color
characterDescription.smile: not smiling in the photo, but lips are slightly pursed, showing a neutral expression
characterDescription.eyebrows: medium thick eyebrows, slightly arched, with a natural dark brown color matching the hair, sparse in some areas
characterDescription.ears: medium-sized ears, close to the head, earlobes appear attached
characterDescription.cheeks: full, round cheeks with a natural rosy blush
characterDescription.chin: softly rounded chin, seamlessly blending into the jawline
characterDescription.facialProportions: large eyes, small nose, and full cheeks create a baby-faced appearance. Eyes are positioned slightly above the horizontal midpoint of the face.
characterDescription.distinctiveFeatures: very fine, almost invisible vellus hair on the upper lip; subtle dark circles underneath eyes; slightly parted lips.
characterDescription.overallImpression: sweet, innocent, and slightly serious appearance, with youthful, baby-like features. The child has a fair complexion and striking blue eyes that stand out.
characterDescription.fullDescription: This is a 5-6 year old child with fair skin and pink undertones, characterized by her striking sky blue almond-shaped eyes with a darker limbal ring. Her dark auburn brown hair is styled in two high pigtail buns with pink clips and loose curls that frame her round face, highlighting her full rosy cheeks. She has a small, slightly upturned nose and medium-sized, rosy pink lips that are slightly pursed in a neutral expression. Additional features include fine vellus hair above the upper lip, and slightly dark circles under the eyes which lends a serious but sweet disposition.
